title: New: p.r.i.n.t.s. – work this out
body:
Can I get away with saying that the beginning of this debut track from LA’s **p.**

**r.i.n.t.s.** sounds quite a lot like Karma Police? Anyway, _work this out_ is a dreamy masterpiece, hinting at touches of 70’s psychedelia, whilst the songwriting itself is much more ‘modern’. Imagine a really sad Best Coast, and you sort of get an idea of what this track is all about. Check it out below.
